\newlabel{fig:countries_ind}{{12}{29}{LLM-use estimates for different countries and language regions for the abstract and main body of the paper. The highest estimate in each panel is marked in a gray box. The estimates for NES and NNES are based on all relevant countries in the dataset, not only those shown here}{figure.caption.13}{}}
